# Keep Docker build contexts lean + reproducible. Applies to all builds (the
# context is the repo root for both the Go API and the dashboard images).
**/node_modules
**/.next
**/dist
**/build
**/out
**/.turbo
**/*.tsbuildinfo
**/coverage
bin/
.git
.github
.DS_Store
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example
# Docs / local infra state — not needed inside images.
docs/
*.md
**/.idea
**/.vscode
minio-data/
.data/
